Without exception, the successful candidate will demonstrate outstanding attention to detail, have excellent problem solving skills, abilities and quality control of the highest standard.&nbsp;The successful candidate will understand and demonstrate how to manage Clients and Projects of International stature.&nbsp;The successful candidate will also demonstrate a deep-seated passion for our organisational culture and brand aspiration of "Greening Africa One Project at a Time"&nbsp;The capacity to diligently, efficiently and effectively manage complex projects, timelines and scenarios will need to be clearly demonstrated as will an inspirational, can-do and people focused leadership ability.&nbsp;Core qualifications, skills sets and experience must include:&nbsp;

